column4: Text
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "752B51864B56083684953DB7A4DCC472", "Have you seen the Lake Guardian?")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "BC8B33C74C988EC8896029B5765F39D6", "If not, you should wait on the south side.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "D1D067894651208FB9D92CAFAB59FBAC", "Get up very early and walk in the mist. Something good will happen!")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "2054E454443A63FDDC0D119074F82BD3", "Did you know there\'s a place in the north called Iceberg Beach?")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "57EABB5A4B31D8F77CF9468B0292DEF5", "Rumor has it that a huge Digimon often appears at the beach.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "A895AE42450D16572E1D0B8C2DAEAF52", "Are the bandits defeated? I heard there is a gang of bandits.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "9E508ABB4D6F965F540980B959D4B855", "Ever been to Great Canyon?")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "74F617A04C2547821FB3E0B911B136A1", "Rumor has it that the bandits are there.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "A6586F2C42A1BBE2EBBED28DD8428BB6", "Are they bad guys?")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "0E94FBA84D544FD60F497E9BEF160A29", "They jump you and rob you.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "59CF52ED4FA4EAA73ADA2EB26B0C6A46", "Ever been to Great Canyon?")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "AA8750C14E7FC0DD4EB828B2299F3A73", "Rumor has it that there is an Invisible Bridge there.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "847A3EC244C08468BE85469E50A2D515", "I hear Machinedramon is back.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "DA86C2CB42C2B3BD79A7DB9028C98C90", "You beat Machinedramon again.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "962B3DCB4277C21D487CC9B89D3A4EA1", "Ok, I\'ll explain to you the surroundings of this city.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "88D36CDB4C3B94ADE3C4C39D3F71D36C", "Native Forest surrounds the city.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "40D44C0D4C9EE5D61248C7B170AD1B0C", "The Digimon around there are not very strong.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "60AC42C04D62544114B1529E5272B38E", "There\'s a Training Camp on the west side. I think you will go there often.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "1D1DE7774F823A649B2E52A4EE07CD60", "Tropical Jungle is on the east side, across the river.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "E0728B964DDBE9620E9AFCB485506160", "I don\'t know what\'s past that.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "637701BD46B2C207107323B7C3E5C09B", "There\'s a mountain and lake on the west side and it\'s a dead end.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "319D3DC84755D576A163A884181FB728", "If you keep going south, there\'s an ocean.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "DAD18BA944A2CC1B478785B31A3030B9", "And there\'s a high mountain in the north. It\'s also a dead end.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "55AAC5DD4AC645F019BE54831E8C3421", "Since this city is the center of the island, there must be vast areas in the north.")
NSLOCTEXT("[2E633A5F44F64638E2766F899F741741]", "6D4502024372F4D44C3650A0D91AEE0C", "I\'ll check out the rumors about the outside area. Come back and find out more.")
